metadata.name: ZHORIK #1
metadata.description:
ZHORIK WANTS OUT!

PERHAPS ONE OF THE MOST MUSICALLY EDUCATED DOG IN THE WORLD. HIS OWNER IS A WELL-KNOWN DJ AND PARTY MAKER (VITALY KOZAK), SO THIS PET UNDERSTANDS MUSIC VERY WELL.

IN THIS WORK IS IMPRINTED PUPPY WHOSE PAWS HAVE PUT IN A SNEAKERS. AS A RESULT - KIND, POSITIVE AND IRONIC IMAGE. THE ORIGINAL BLACK-AND-WHITE CIRCULATION DID NOT SUFFICIENTLY CONVEY THE INNER BRIGHTNESS AND THEREFORE DIFFERENT COLOURS AND COLLAGES OF PAPER WERE CREATED.
